data.meta_description: Read the obituary of Robert Wilson Keller (1938 - 2013) from Grant, AL. Leave your condolences and send flowers to the family to show you care.
data.text: Robert Wilson Keller, age 75, of Guntersville, AL, formerly of Grant, AL, passed away on Friday, November 29, 2013. He was born February 18, 1938 to Jess and Vera Keller. Funeral services for Mr. Keller were Sunday, December 1, 2013, 2:00... View Obituary & Service Information
